|CKBThe Confidence's Dubiously Official Roll|000

Syntax: cwho
Alias:  charlatans

List the visible Charlatans currently abroad. The roll includes reputation,
dominant road, present activity, and whatever credential the clerk invented
for that Rank.

Road callings include Misdirector, Volatilist, Contrabandist, Eclectic, and
Undeclared. "Incognito" means the Charlatan line is muffed, not that the
member has become especially subtle.
